Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteScanCell(25.10)                                    deleteScanCell(25.10)

Name
       deleteScanCell  -  Removes  the  scan cell specification from a library
       cell

Syntax
       deleteScanCell

       [-help]

       [<cellName>]

       Removes the scan cell specification from a library cell.  This  command
       can  be called after importing design if there are scan cell specifica-
       tions in library; or else it can be used after specifyScanCell.

Parameters
       <cellName>
              Specifies the cell from which to remove the scan specification.

Example
       The following command removes the  scan  specification  from  the  cell
       named FF_SCAN:

       deleteScanCell FF_SCAN

